  "tips": [
    "Located in the heart of the Selva de Irati, this site is a classic route and tourist recognized for its charm. There you have a bar, restaurant, a bike shop and a water fountain, as well as being surrounded by a beautiful setting in the heart of the Navarrese Pyrenees.",
    "Nice road on the France-Spain border in the heart of the Navarrese Pyrenees and surrounded by a wonderful grove of trees, ideal in the hot months to ride under the shade.",
    "Wonderful gravel track that runs close to the Ibarrondoa ravine in the heart of the Navarrese Pyrenees and very close to the border between Spain and France.",
    "This wonderful reservoir located in the Pyrenees area is a place you cannot miss. Surrounded by a dense beech forest, you can get here by a picturesque path, an ideal walk for the whole family,"
  ],
